OL,6,FA prison officer who had an
OL,7,Finappropriate relationship with an
OL,8,Finmate has been given a suspended
OL,9,Fsentence.
OL,11,FMegan Breen, 23, worked at Usk and
OL,12,FPrescoed prisons in Gwent when the
OL,13,Frelationship took place in 2022.
OL,15,FCardiff Crown Court heard that this
OL,16,Frelationship came to light when Breen
OL,17,Fwas talking with a fellow prison
OL,18,Fofficer in 2022.
