OL,3,CPrison officer who had relationship
OL,4,Cwith inmate given suspended sentence
OL,6,FShe told the colleague that she'd
OL,7,Fslept with an inmate after arranging
OL,8,Fto meet him while he was on weekend
OL,9,Frelease in Liverpool and she was in
OL,10,Fthe city to celebrate her 20th
OL,11,Fbirthday.
OL,13,FWhen Breen made this confession, her
OL,14,Fcolleague asked her if she understood
OL,15,Fthe consequences of her actions.
OL,17,FShe replied: "Yeah - five years. But
OL,18,Fno one is going to tell anyone."
OL,20,FBreen was suspended from her duties
OL,21,Fthe next day.
