OL,6,FWhen police seized her phone and the
OL,7,Fprison issue phone belonging to the
OL,8,Fprisoner, they discovered 558 messages
OL,9,Fexchanged between the pair.
OL,11,FThese messages, the court heard,
OL,12,Fconfirmed a "close, personal, romantic
OL,13,Frelationship" between Breen and the
OL,14,Fprisoner, who was serving four years
OL,15,Ffor conspiracy to supply Class A drugs.
OL,17,FNow a victim impact statement by the
OL,18,Fgovernor of HMP Prescoed, the open
OL,19,Fjail where the prisoner was serving
OL,20,Fhis sentence, was read out in court.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/5
