OL,6,FRobert Denman said that the operation
OL,7,Fof the prison system depended on
OL,8,F"proper and appropriate relationships
OL,9,Fbetween staff and prisoners".
OL,11,FAnd that cases like this fell "far
OL,12,Fbelow the standards of behaviour for
OL,13,Fofficers rightfully expected by the
OL,14,Fpublic".
OL,16,FBreen pleaded guilty to a charge of
OL,17,Fmisconduct in public office.
