OL,6,FJudge Tracey Lloyd-Clarke told Breen
OL,7,Fthat her pregnancy and the fact she
OL,8,Falready had a one-year-old son made
OL,9,Fthis an "exceptional" case and that a
OL,10,Fsuspended sentence was therefore
OL,11,Fappropriate.
OL,13,FShe was sentenced to 10 months in jail
OL,14,Fsuspended for 18 months and ordered to
OL,15,Fcarry out rehabilitation activity.
